data.meta_description: Andrew II Of Hungary was born in the year 1176 in Esztergom, Komarom-Esztergom, Hungary, son of Bela Harmadik Hungary and Agnes DeChatillon. He was married in the year 1215 in Esztergom, Komarom-Esztergom, Hungary to Yolande DeCourtenay, they gave birth to 1 child. He died on September 21, 1235 in Eger, Heves, Hungary. This information is part of Mort Family Tree by Susan L Mort on Genealogy Online.
